Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:22.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天悄悄许下的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:27.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被封闭着静止不动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:32.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹如梦境般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:38.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描画了出色的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:44.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未来等待  想象那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.59,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加无法入眠 并非没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:52.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次相遇发生奇迹般的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:53.62,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:56.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:59.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:01.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在星空飞扬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高歌源于勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:06.69,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深不可测的价值观
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:16.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的人物从不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:26.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路标一定直指前方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:27.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空の赤と長く伸びた影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:31.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつの間にか　二番星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:36.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰のためそして何のために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:40.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この限りない世界はある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:50.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは　あ～　答えを聞くためではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:58.44,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ　ここにいる一人の人が繋がれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:02.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全な世界　みんな会いで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:08.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない世界　自分を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:12.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放て　希望の矢を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:16.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ　叶いとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:21.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全な世界　みんな会いで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:26.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない世界　自分を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:31.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放せ　闇の影を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:35.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ　見えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:27.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤色夜空 长长延伸的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:31.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候出现了第二颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:36.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了谁 又是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:40.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这无边无际的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:50.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是　啊 不是为了寻求答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:58.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 如果能和这里的一个人相连
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:02.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完美世界 我们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:08.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的世界 我们了解了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:12.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出希望之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:16.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 即便能够实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:21.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完美世界 我们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:26.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的世界 我们了解了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:31.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放黑暗的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:35.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是还没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:37.47,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆一行在旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个叫杰达·拉科斯帕的圣职者相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.90,0:01:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰达性情善良 而且还是个大力士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而巴隆一行对他的行动却一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这样还是和他一起与占领村子的僵尸战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临别时巴隆一行和他约定再会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后向着新的城镇出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:05.02,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,238)}暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:05.02,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(376,392)}鬼神的眼睛也会流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 就是这个路程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这样的小姑娘在 真是被治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 离城镇还远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说达库里斯镇是最近的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在你们还是别去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个城镇不安定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有传言说有鬼神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫罗克希的鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希是那个鬼剑士的罗克希吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对鬼剑士罗克希有兴趣吗 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉德大陆中传说中的女剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过听说已经死了很长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的还真是详细啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老夫对可爱的通吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫我可是什么都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据传 罗克希是巨乳而且喜欢男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时拥有不计其数男人的了不得的黑毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 那家伙还真是了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的 谎言 谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信这个老头儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷 要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 要去达库里斯镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这点小事没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点去抓那个冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪是我啊 一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是鬼剑士罗克希只有你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是背黑锅啊 给我做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是快乐的旅行 年轻人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此分别吧 我会想你们的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去铲除鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁太阳还没落山 必须去采购了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也该换一件新衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情 就别找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 应该还有点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事 分开行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 即使挖地三尺也要把那家伙找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的倒容易
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到底藏在什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赶得上还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬼神流泪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说是冒牌的罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样 也是被厌恶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又要假冒罗克希之名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继承了鬼剑士罗克希之名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:06:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士罗克希是心灵的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想变成罗克希那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要不要加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够给你罗克希之名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体已经
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 所以才来邀请你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们见识一下你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是条件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败一个嚣张的鬼剑士 对你来说很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢 听说闹得挺厉害的 不过没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和杀人的鬼神扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 你也是鬼剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到线索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的还在这个镇上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了 冒牌罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用这把罗克希之剑杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是罗克沙诺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我是一个村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得这么强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才这种程度 看来还没有鬼神化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经鬼神化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经只能以鬼神的身份活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能够回头的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好用你的眼睛看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南来北往的客官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走过路过不要错过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的表演很精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未完待续的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEY BABY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在我的怀中撒娇 哭泣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太接近我的话 心也会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有鬼神出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现鬼神了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼神 莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方已经无药可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你做罗克希的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你吗 罗克沙诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我们 老头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不让你吃点苦头你是不会明白的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这老头儿怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那个老爷子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁 你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快去救那个小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他也变成鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的对手是老夫 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道老夫的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点本事吗 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有人盯上了鬼剑士 是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到我说的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊 那家伙已经不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不救他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止我们不是被巴隆救过好多次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我们来救他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我救 我救就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务艰巨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让他安定下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快冻住他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒悲鸣洞穴那里的那家伙之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就都全部结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这之前 我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是你在救我 这次换我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿甘多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让这些孩子留下那样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给我力量吧 阿甘多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人流泪就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的份 巴隆的份都由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流泪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伊鲁贝克大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要杀罗克沙诺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也像她一样没有去处被人类厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收留这样的我的不就是你吗伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克沙诺流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就此了结她对她来说或许更加幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再出现那样的鬼神我们所应走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我在意的还有另外一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人的力量不可小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵啊 再让我多睡一会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会为你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次真是累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷 你的胳膊没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心老夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁束器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老夫的朋友特制的羁束器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给需要的人是最合适不过的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗克沙诺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了 变得很精神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然从那个状态回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是靠自己的力量回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有人代替你流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下个城镇之前我的行李就归你负责没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃这么多的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次没买新衣服以后慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一遍 再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没说 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个羁束器已经交给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受阿甘多所托好不容易把羁束器带给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个羁束器应该给还有未来的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老夫早点找到你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命就
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 从变身为鬼神的那一刻起这种事早就注定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我现在很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在我生命的最后见到了巴隆和罗克希
